<Defs>
	<ThingDef ParentName="DrugBase">
		<defName>AC_IcedElixir</defName>
		<label>iced elixir</label>
		<description>A crystalline draught brewed from frost leaves. It hums with a biting cold, said to sharpen the senses, steady the hand, and leave a lingering trail of winter across the tongue. Excessive consumption can lead to alcohol blackouts and, over time, addiction.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Trade considerations:&lt;/color&gt;\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Ingredients:&lt;/color&gt; Making 15 iced elixir requires 150 frost leaves for a total value of 15, and sells for 10.30, giving a &lt;color=#33CC33&gt;90.29%&lt;/color&gt; profit per unit (very high, as the leaves can't be cultivated).\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Fermentation time:&lt;/color&gt; 5 days.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Caravan trading:&lt;/color&gt; Its weight is 0.3 Kg, for a value per Kg of &lt;color=#33CC33&gt;34.33&lt;/color&gt;.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Profit per day:&lt;/color&gt; On average, profit per day is &lt;color=#33CC33&gt;1.86&lt;/color&gt; (for reference, Yayo is 0.35).</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks>
			<HediffDef>AlcoholHigh</HediffDef>
